Class: ALL<br />
Race: ALL<br />
Slot type 7:empty<br />

</p>
</blockquote> 
<p>
Items given to you by Grimel:
</p>
<blockquote> 
<p>
<b><a href="/items/show_item.php?item=9411&menustr=">Portable Drink Barrel</a></b><br />
Container: CLOSED.<br />
LORE ITEM NO DROP <br />
